  "3188970": {
    "name": "Elemental War Clash",
    "steam_appid": 3188970,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/15dd5bbd22b162425fdb142a4db15c4d.poster.avif?t=1761559581\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/15dd5bbd22b162425fdb142a4db15c4d.webm?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/15dd5bbd22b162425fdb142a4db15c4d.mp4?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elemental War Clash》将经典塔防游戏与 roguelite 和 RPG 机制以及不同元素相结合，创造出更强大的塔楼。作为《元素战争 1》和《元素战争 2》的集大成者，《元素战争冲突》提供了最丰富的内容、最出色的功能和最震撼的视觉效果，您可以打败自己的传送门，在 PvP 中击败其他玩家，或在关卡编辑器中创建新地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/7851212e884bcaf0e1e7c28dd9a4fe3b.poster.avif?t=1761559581\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/7851212e884bcaf0e1e7c28dd9a4fe3b.webm?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/7851212e884bcaf0e1e7c28dd9a4fe3b.mp4?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素战争》的基础是不同的元素。通过每五波获得的元素水晶，您可以召唤出强大的 BOSS，即所谓的元素。击败元素后，您就可以解锁它们的元素，从而改善您的防御塔，并通过组合最多三种元素来获得新的能力和升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/12051edd355b46baa4089965041d2ffc.poster.avif?t=1761559581\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/12051edd355b46baa4089965041d2ffc.webm?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/12051edd355b46baa4089965041d2ffc.mp4?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素战争》系列的核心是任务和物品。通过完成任务，您可以为物品池解锁新的物品，这些物品会在您的整个游戏过程中掉落。物品可以是被动能量、主动能力或定制防御塔的防御塔装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/52fe6287bfbf7106f354d239144f893e.poster.avif?t=1761559581\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/52fe6287bfbf7106f354d239144f893e.webm?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188970/extras/52fe6287bfbf7106f354d239144f893e.mp4?t=1761559581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素战争冲突》具有跨平台 PvP 多人游戏模式 “冲突”，在该模式中，两名玩家将进行对战。你们既要保卫自己的传送门，又要同时向对手发送怪物。谁能活得最久？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种不同能力和强度的防御塔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 种单人模式： 英雄模式、经典模式和生存模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的被动和主动道具以及防御塔装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 “淘金热 ”到 “无敌 ”等怪物能力，让每次运行都独一无二</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从沙漠到冰雪世界，环境各异，视觉效果极佳</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的技能，多种升级，自定义你的游戏行为</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量不同的怪物和元素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多个任务可解锁新物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡编辑器可创建和共享新地图</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 德语, 法语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 乌克兰语, 匈牙利语",
